      "releaseNotes": "Say hello to one of our biggest releases yet! :)\n\n- Dumbify now supports up to 3 widgets! So you can add more apps to your minimalist Home Screen without it feeling too crowded.\n\n- We've added a spacer widget so that you can centre your launcher widget in the middle of the screen! Along with that, we've added a setting to allow you to vertically, align your widget at the top, centre or bottom. We will be adding further customizability to the spacer widget in the near future!\n\n- We've updated all our tutorial videos to make them easier to understand!\n\n- We've made it easier for users to learn how to enable quick launch! So your apps can launch quicker with Dumbify.\n\n- Some users were encountering some problems when setting up dumbify, we've added some tutorials for Common Issues you may encounter.\n\n- General UX improvements + Bug Fixes\n\nWe hope that you continue to enjoy Dumbify and the minimalist, distraction free experience it provides! :)",
